wikipedia_page.main: Thomas Webb (born 17 April 1989) is an English footballer who plays as a forward for Tilbury. He was a product of the Colchester United Academy, going on to make one first-team substitute appearance for the club. He has also represented Folkestone Invicta, Halstead Town, East Thurrock United and AFC Sudbury.
